===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|にじ|alt=霓}}
{{IPAfont|⟨nizi⟩}} → {{IPAchar|/niʑi/}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|虹|tr=nizi}}, ultimately from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*nonsi}}. First attested in the ''{{w|Kojiki}}'' of 712 {{CE}}.<ref name="NKD">{{R:Nihon Kokugo Daijiten Concise|虹・霓}}</ref>

Also attested as man’yōgana form {{m|ja||爾自}} in the {{m|ja||金光明最勝王経音義|tr=Konkōmyō Saishōō-kyō Ongi}} of 1079. May be a shift from earlier {{m|ojp|ぬじ|tr=nuji}} or {{m|ojp|のじ|tr=noji}} readings.

